{"tid":303780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴係江派打手？","createTime":"2017-06-30T12:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T15:05:15.000Z","uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fb1752e0570c4ee32266131ccc75c84233f1f7","tid":303780,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:10:58.000Z","msg":"我硬係覺得郭文貴係江派打手 江派眼見習大大同王歧山聯盟得天下<br />\n於是開始派人煽風點火 之前片入面所講嘅老領導好似係江派啲特務？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有研究郭文貴究竟係咩人咁把炮<br />\n定係佢都係江派啲特務？<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/201008_b91b62fddad2fa41452a04a2f94f461e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F201008_b91b62fddad2fa41452a04a2f94f461e.jpg&h=3d7af5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n題外話:阿叔黎講佢都幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f2f4d0d7c756db6bfbb36e6931246c0e94e25d","tid":303780,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"邊個打手都唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2ec3a71e5e441586a923d022e814c3cc7d7b2b","tid":303780,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"江澤民有咩唔好<br />\n佢揸旗果陣中國最自由開放"},{"pid":"f1c5a0ddd1acf7ee62c3252bec673c3c040699b8","tid":303780,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"唔係咁搞笑啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n江派重有邊個擔旗"},{"pid":"f84bcfc2fdc78d1937898efd892cd7ae00e2a1a0","tid":303780,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>江澤民有咩唔好<br />\n佢揸旗果陣中國最自由開放</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔反對呢個講法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但成個意義就唔同左<br />\n可能唔會有支爆發生